1. Purpose

IX-CognitionKernel is made source-available so that interested parties may
inspect the project, review its technical structure, and perform limited
noncommercial evaluation to decide whether to contact the copyright holder about
a separate commercial or operational license.

IX-CognitionKernel is a research prototype and governed causal cognition project.
It is not represented as artificial general intelligence, certified artificial
general intelligence, production-ready autonomy, safety-certified software,
security-certified software, procurement-ready software, or an independently
validated AGI system.

This license does not grant open-source rights. It does not grant permission for
